      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. With a flawless exterior and an interior that feels brand new, this is a rare find for anyone seeking perfection on wheels!",
